{"tid":1478890,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"各位新舊連登用戶請誰，呢個壞習慣係會影響到日後運動！","createTime":"2019-08-16T16:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T17:13:30.000Z","uid":49936,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"459bbd8760e209ee7d8cdf1c99bfe55d2f04183a","tid":1478890,"uid":49936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:37:57.000Z","msg":"我法國唔少巴絲同連登都有個<span style=\"color: red;\">壞習慣</span>！就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">懶！</span></span><br />\n所以我會宣揚如何正確使用連登！<br />\n<br />\n壞習慣包括<br />\n- 只看標題<br />\n- 只看正負評數<br />\n- 只看熱門回覆<br />\n- 只看樓主內容<br />\n- 只看熱門post<br />\n唔好睇小以上習慣，<span style=\"color: pink;\">往往風向撚標題撚成功，就係有你地既助攻</span><br />\n<br />\n但係要改善，係十分簡單！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">- 多睇即時post<br />\n- 睇完樓主內容，一定要睇埋其他comment<br />\n- 善用不推文回覆</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">818</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0b94a0a8b26c6017e62374ff6abd064437ed98","tid":1478890,"uid":49936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:38:45.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"4eee52a5468887a5bd5df2f5f169769cab54beea","tid":1478890,"uid":49936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0389cb6ebffe02e6f115941f92dfd6c3a6b60639","tid":1478890,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08